						href="#/catalog-recipes">Catalog Recipes</a> section and follow the upgrade wizard.<br/>
					If you already updated your <b>catalog recipes</b> and still see this warning then execute operation
					<b>Redeploy Service</b> on every deployed service.
				</alert>
			</div>
			<div ng-if="myNginx && (!myEnvironment.protocol || !myEnvironment.port)">
				<alert type="warning">
					<h3 style="margin-top: 0">Warning</h3>
					<hr>
					Detected an old style deployment for this environment. Make sure you pull the latest images of SOAJS
